16:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認真 我話你知點贏.......</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034206</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"261504d67a87b5d8899f237f34872348d196aabe","tid":2034394,"uid":224106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"支持新加坡回歸中國<br />\n做個中國人<br />\n<br />\n中共一定錫曬你"},{"pid":"5c9291563df3de37e62ef48e06b4e7dc99e20e9a","tid":2034394,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"香港仆街, 大把資金會走去新加坡"},{"pid":"63a327f096a307b30b63464993fcc0555df4c379","tid":2034394,"uid":209888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"Monkeypore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a17107cf1cf6fe8497a2cb0a69de9559f61c7b","tid":2034394,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:22:57.000Z","msg":"明框屌尻一國兩制從一開始就冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋笑尻支那係管唔到國際城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，下下都話係因為示威者引起而成既結果又或者話香港人唔信支那。倒不如係話so call狼式精英管治係香港唔撚WORK，因為遠比支那同港共聰明既精英唔會buy你個套。除非有雙普選，如果唔係則使經濟幾撚好，國家認同幾撚高都好，都係唔會立到23條。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢篇文比台灣人睇，相信留言既會係認同呢篇文既角度比較多。"},{"pid":"1348fb9bf8f7d5636ab0f969408fa3ceb34bc460","tid":2034394,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"風涼話，新加坡暗爽"},{"pid":"7fc3a58c8ab28a362c51efdbe60dbad8a7399c2f","tid":2034394,"uid":17125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rV21oei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrV21oei.jpg&h=1f9a375d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd17a8729418adf05ab4f892a53e74eef45ff98e","tid":2034394,"uid":232382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"即將車毁人忙，無剎車掣唧明明係習近平統治下嘅中國大陸<br />\n個作者調轉嚟講都有嘅"},{"pid":"522690a3f48436c8635109a37a7fdfcebe44e88b","tid":2034394,"uid":197976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"有啲point我覺得佢係講得啱嘅<br />\n1. 港共根本冇能力管治香港<br />\n2. 中共其實根本唔想一國兩制<br />\n3. 香港同中共有根本上矛盾冇可能兩制並存<br />\n4. 香港未來好取決於中國/美國行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分別只係作者將重點放響我地加速結束一國兩制係唔合理唔應該(+港共太無能幫唔到中共搞獨裁)，<br />\n而我地就覺得係中共控制欲太強先係一國兩制殺手咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果然獨裁政權角度同正常人有啲唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfbd88e727f24da91625b7c6b5add9324d9ad21","tid":2034394,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"Monkey"},{"pid":"cf39f68ca2d51065a4ef43c89e95b799cead4731","tid":2034394,"uid":232382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46fa9493700060cd3c747b259b82e2e72aa35afe","tid":2034394,"uid":44646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3f1cbadec177808d2dccbea5d0223383abcb476e","tid":2034394,"uid":173179,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"果然係冇人睇你hl既部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"不無道理<br />\n重點：中共為保權，已經唔會去計經濟損失<br />\n<br />\n對我方而言，攬炒手段已達成<br />\n但對家唔妥協<br />\n要想下一步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"賭外資走唔走<br />\n賭埋外資走咗中資仲可以利用香港吸水 <br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得未攬炒完，可以再勁啲"}],"pinned":{"pid":"b071652122620ff0dd48c2c09a9dafe9f3f06878","tid":2034394,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"又係白宮聯署: 港版國安法一成立,